adderall.name: Bottle Of Adderall
adderall.desc: To certain populations, this stuff is worth its weight in gold. Can be used to numb the effects of ADHD.

anno_car.name: Anno's Car
anno_car.desc: The Apocalypse Nirvana is a rugged electric vehicle designed for eco-friendly off-road adventures. Anno wanted one solely because of its kick-ass name.

anno_phone.name: Anno's Phone
anno_phone.desc: An An(no)droid phone with a Nirvana case on it. If there's anyone that can be classified as the #1 Nirvana fan, it's probably Anno.

apple_pie.name: Hot Apple Pie
apple_pie.desc: It's totally store-bought, but that's okay.

billy_car.name: Billy's Car
billy_car.desc: A 2008 Land Rover LR3 that was featured in the infomercial for the Jupiter Jack.

blank_car.name: Blank's Car
blank_car.desc: A modded 2012 Honda Civic. While most of the changes Blank has made to the car do not affect its appearance, some notable additions include a built-in backup camera, front {i}and{/i} rear dashcams, and a secondary truck air horn.

blank_speaker.name: Big Subwoofer
blank_speaker.desc: A Dayton Audio SUB-1200 12-inch 120-watt powered subwoofer. If you want high-fidelity bass, this will probably cover all your... bases.

carrot_cake.name: Carrot Cake
carrot_cake.desc: A moist cake made from carrots. Most people either love it or hate it.

cheap_shelf.name: Cheap-Ass Garage Shelf
cheap_shelf.desc: It does the job, as long as you don't jostle it in any way...

colt.name: Colt .45 Revolver
colt.desc: As he nears retirement, the Sheriff secretly just wanted his trusted side-arm to go to someone who would appreciate it. Either that, or he dropped it into his gift box without realizing it.

cop_car.name: Copguy's Cruiser
cop_car.desc: While there are many like it, this one is his.

crotch_doctor.name: Crotch Doctor
crotch_doctor.desc: All jokes aside, it's actually a decent product. Carguy just needs to work on his sales pitch.

cs_cold_hat.name: Cirrus Hat
cs_cold_hat.desc: Is it a cloud that's a cat, or a cat that's a cloud?

cs_id.name: CS' ID Card
cs_id.desc: He should probably get one with an updated photo...

cs_phone.name: CS' Cellphone
cs_phone.desc: While purple isn't CS' favorite color, there's no denying that this phone is stylish!

cs_wallet.name: CS' Wallet
cs_wallet.desc: While he may have missed out on the PUMA × {i}Tetris{/i} shoe collab, at least CS copped this sweet wallet at Hot Topic.

cutting_board.name: Cutting Board
cutting_board.desc: CS doesn't own a cutting board, so the president brought one made of the finest oak.

d20.name: 20-Sided Die
d20.desc:
Since CS doesn't play tabletop games, there's no telling where this came from.
I wonder what would happen if he rolled it again.

decor_boxes.name: Boxes Of Christmas Décor
decor_boxes.desc: Filled with ornaments, wreaths, {a=https://youtu.be/gS4CeZ4H_E4?t=41}wiggly trees{/a}, and more!

digi_nugget.name: The Nugget
digi_nugget.desc: Digi's personal spacecraft. It's been through a lot, taking Digi around the galaxy and being hastily-repaired by them along the way. Iris has insisted they upgrade to ion thrusters.

dog_food.name: Bag Of Dog Food
dog_food.desc: But... why would you bring dog food to a gift exchange...?

doi.name: Declaration Of Independence
doi.desc: Wait, how the hell is the president allowed to just {i}give{/i} this away?!

festive_bag.name: Festive Bag
festive_bag.desc: One of many seasonal items CS picked up at Michael's.

flashlight_held.name: Flashlight
flashlight_held.desc: A very important part of any emergency kit.

gamersupps.name: Canister Of Gamer Supps
gamersupps.desc: If you're not into "Guacamole Gamer Fart 9000", Gamer Supps offers a variety of other delightful flavors, including "Titty Milk" and "Grandpa's Ashes" {a=https://gamersupps.gg/collections/caffeine-free}(yes, {i}really){/a}.{/i}

handy_switch.name: Handy Switch
handy_switch.desc: While advertised as a convenient-to-place light switch, if you put electrical tape over the light sensor, you can use it for anything that'll plug into a wall.

hard_drive.name: 1TB Hard Drive
hard_drive.desc: Plug random hard drives into your PC at your own risk.

instant_pot.name: Instant Pot
instant_pot.desc: An ideal gift for anyone who loves cooking, but {i}hates{/i} standing over a stovetop.

joj_ufo.name: JoJ UFO
joj_ufo.desc: The primary mode of transportation for HoH SiS. Allows for safe traversal over even the most unstable foundations. This particular model also includes a laser defense system.

lego_train.name: Lego Train Set
lego_train.desc: Mean was {i}very{/i} tempted to keep this for himself...

letter.name: CS' invitation
letter.owner: Everybody who showed up to the party
letter.desc: An invitation to a grand party with festivities galore.

lights_box.name: Box Of Christmas Lights
lights_box.desc: An absolute mess of garland and strands of lights. Why would you put {i}two{/i} long tangle-prone items in the same box? You know they make spools for storing these now, right?

ltt_bottle.name: LTT Water Bottle
ltt_bottle.desc: This particular bottle boasts a colorway that has since been discontinued. {a=https://lttstore.com}lttstore.com{/a} {size=-24}(not sponsored){/size}

ltt_car.name: Linus' Car
ltt_car.desc: Known as "The Lambo", this is an early-2000s Honda Civic that was {i}originally{/i} black, but was repainted (badly) in {a=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RU87dFB9yKI}{i}Boss' Car Gets Painted Pink.{/i}{/a}

ltt_screwdriver.name: LTT Screwdriver
ltt_screwdriver.desc: This collaborative effort with Megapro promises to deliver a top-of-the-line screwdriving experience. {a=https://lttstore.com}lttstore.com{/a} {size=-24}(not sponsored){/size}

mashed_potatoes.name: Mashed Potatoes
mashed_potatoes.desc: A holiday favorite, even for those relatives who don't have all their teeth.

mean_train.name: Mean's Locomotive
mean_train.desc: Mean's personal steam engine. Nobody really knows how he managed to acquire an entire {i}train,{/i} but this old locomotive has been lovingly restored to its former glory. It also matches Mean's jacket splendidly.

mgs1.name: {i}Metal Gear Solid
mgs1.desc: The 1998 Hideo game that spawned a now-million-dollar franchise and started the trend of producing a title that is more cutscene than game.

nog.name: Bottle Of Eggnog
nog.desc: While the exact origins of the drink are debated, most historians agree that eggnog originated in medieval Britain.

obama_chopper.name: Presidential Chopper
obama_chopper.desc: A U.S. UH-60L Black Hawk, one of many government-owned vehicles at the president's disposal.

old_coins.name: Old Coins
old_coins.desc: These appear to have been minted in 1850.

old_shirt.name: Old T-Shirt
old_shirt.desc: A leftover shirt from CS' closet cleanout {a=https://www.depop.com/cs188/}Depop{/a} sale.

oxygen_canister.name: Oxygen Canister
oxygen_canister.desc: Make sure to keep one of these on hand just in case your teacher ever asks you to {a=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z1cfVQyrQ3Q}stop breathing.{/a}

peach_syrup.name: Can Of Peach Syrup
peach_syrup.desc: Try spreading it on toast or crumpets, enjoying it by the spoonful, {a=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlfJx1aDmR4&t=11s}stick a finger in and lick it, or even lift it up and drink a bit.{/a} Your secrets are safe here.

peppermint_bark.name: Peppermint Bark
peppermint_bark.desc: A sweet Christmas treat that might just break your teeth!

pie.name: Premade Apple Pie
pie.desc: Not as good as homemade, but these are a godsend when you are short on time and need to feed a crowd.

pills.name: Bottle Of Pain Pills
pills.desc: Always remember to keep track of all of your prescription medications.

pipe_gun.name: Pipe Gun
pipe_gun.desc: It's held together with duct tape, rope, and a prayer, but it gets the job done.

potato_bag.name: Bag Of Potatoes
potato_bag.desc: Boil 'em, mash 'em, stick 'em in a stew!

pringles.name: Pizza Pringles
pringles.desc: Possibly the best flavor of Pringles.

projector.name: Projector
projector.desc: This inexpensive projector is proof that five-star reviews are not always a reliable indicator of quality.

rental_car.name: Rental Car
rental_car.desc: A cheap sedan with a whole lot of miles on it.

riffmaster.name: Riffmaster
riffmaster.desc: A highly sought-after controller among rhythm game enthusiasts.

roll_and_rocker.name: Roll & Rocker
roll_and_rocker.desc: An obscure NES accessory that is better off left in the past.

rolling_rock.name: Bottle Of Rolling Rock
rolling_rock.desc: A Pennsylvania classic since 1939. Well, until it was bought out in 2006, anyway. {a=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rolling_Rock}(Source){/a}

russian_radio.name: Soviet Radio
russian_radio.desc: A relic of a great, terrible, and rather chilly war.

santa_sleigh.name: Santa's Sleigh
santa_sleigh.desc: There probably isn't a single vehicle on Earth that has more miles on it than {i}this{/i} one.

runaway_bus.name: The Bus
runaway_bus.desc: Rumored to be owned by a traveling jazz band that has been performing around the country since the 90s.

shopping_cart.name: Shopping Cart
shopping_cart.desc: CS' local Target uses different carts than most other stores. You can't stand on the little bar at the bottom and ride it around like a scooter. Thankfully, the familiar metal chassis can be found at most other locations.

shovel.name: CS' Shovel
shovel.desc: In the dead of winter, it's a northerner's best friend.

small_city_slider.name: Small Town Slider
small_city_slider.desc: An even smaller mini-burger for your even smaller holiday guests.

snacks.name: Pile Of Snacks
snacks.desc: An assortment of random snacks that CS had in his pantry. He put them out with the purpose of making the holiday spread look bigger than it actually is.

snow_pile.name: Snow Pile
snow_pile.desc: But is it a snow poff?

spray_cheese.name: Can Of Easy Cheese
spray_cheese.desc: Invented in the 1960s and advertised as a party snack, this feat of engineering is able to dispense cheese product even if the can is sprayed while upside-down. {a=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Easy_Cheese}(Source){/a}

sunny_d.name: Bottle Of Sunny D
sunny_d.desc: Don't drink too much of this, or you'll start looking like a {a=https://web.archive.org/web/20071213095714/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/wales/578945.stm}{i}Simpsons{/i} character{/a}.

target_bags.name: Target Grocery Bags
target_bags.desc:
Illegal in at least 12 states and 500 cities... including New York?!

Hey, wait a minute--!

tate_phone.name: Tate's Cellphone
tate_phone.desc: It has been modified to allow a cute charm to be attached.

tato_bag.name: Bag Of Potatoes...?
tato_bag.desc:
There is something peculiar about these...

Hey, does anyone else hear screaming?

thigh_highs.name: Thigh-High Socks
thigh_highs.desc: For warm legs without the movement restrictions of pants, nothing beats a nice pair of programming socks.

tree_box.name: Christmas Tree Box
tree_box.desc: Big, heavy, and waterproof. Guaranteed to keep your artificial Christmas tree in tip-top shape, year after year.
